<pc>。</pc>契丹攻北唐河<pc>，</pc>大將<persName>李繼隆</persName>遣部將逆戰<pc>，</pc>為敵所乘<pc>。</pc>奄至水南<pc>。</pc>敏以<measure quantity="100" unit="riders">
